**`backend/main.py`**
- Imported `AUTH_REQUIRED_PAGES`
- Added middleware check: if path is in `AUTH_REQUIRED_PAGES` and no session, redirect to `/login`

**`backend/apis/jobs.py`**
- Added `request: Request` param to `create_job`
- Added `get_session` call at the top — returns 401 if unauthenticated
